      <title>LBS Notification System</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/documentation/api/notification/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 14:23:54 -0300</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/documentation/api/notification/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;method&#34;&gt;Method:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-c#&#34; data-lang=&#34;c#&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; MessageNotify(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; message, LogType logType = LogType.Log, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; duration = &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;To display notifications in the tool use the LBSMainWindow&amp;rsquo;s MessageNotify static function:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Message:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;String&lt;/code&gt; Text that&amp;rsquo;ll be shown on screen.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LogType:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;enum Logtype,Log&lt;/code&gt; The type of message, it affects the icon displayed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;code&gt;int&lt;/code&gt; The duration in seconds of the message before it fades out and it&amp;rsquo;s deleted.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;example&#34;&gt;Example:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-c#&#34; data-lang=&#34;c#&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;LBSMainWindow.instance.MessageNotify(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;[ISI Lab] Warning: You don&amp;#39;t have any layer selected.&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, LogType.Warning, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;notification result&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a6d5c9eb-411c-49b1-ac25-4374b981d536&#34; title=&#34;A sample notification&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
